::Rex/Firearm::

Rex looks at Imprisoner. "Sorry about that," he says as they head toward the 
brig, him and Firearm holding their weapons ready as the internal defences 
monitor the prisoners, "Firearm's neural circuitry is a bit primitive."

"PRIMITIVE?!" Firearm objects, then calming down as Rex nods.
